      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I think the issue might be that we have huge piles of seasonal stuff just sitting in the backroom not moving at all. It feels like we're just accumulating a bunch of stuff we can't use. What are some specific ways to fix a low ratio if I notice we have a lot of dead stock just sitting there?",
